('CIVE261', 'Materials and Structural Behavior I ', 'Introduces the basic materials of construction (timber, masonry, steel, and concrete). Covers their behavior as ingredients of the structural system. Required for architecture and construction management students. Fall.', 3.00, 'CIVE', 0.00, NULL),
